<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, January 6 (Xinhua) -- Afghanistan's ruling Taliban
Thursday bombed with jets opposition-held areas to the north of
the capital of Kabul, news reaching here quoted Taliban sources as
saying.
</P>
