77 kilometers north of Kabul and on nearby areas, he said.
</P>
<P>
The Taliban Islamic militia, holding over 80 percent of the
territory in the war-torn Afghanistan, have been battling
opposition forces led by former Defense Minister Ahmed Masood,
which control tracts of territory in the northeast. 
