Today's ordination of five bishops suits the needs of church
development and the desire of the broad masses of Chinese
Catholics, Liu said.
</P>
<P>
In the new century, he said, the Chinese church will continue
to adhere to the principles of independence and patriotism.
</P>
<P>
Chinese church figures show that at present there are nearly 5
million Catholics in the country and some 5,000 Catholic churches.
